1. On *kaže* da će doći kasnije. (He says he will come later.)
2. *Kazeš* da ti nije stalo, ali tvoje oči govore drugačije. (You say you don't care, but your eyes tell a different story.)
3. Ja *kažem* da je to loša ideja. (I say that's a bad idea.)
4. Oni *kažu* da će biti sunčano sutra. (They say it will be sunny tomorrow.)
5. Da li si *rekao* Ivanu šta se dogodilo? (*Kazao* sam mu sinoć.)(Did you tell Ivan what happened? (I *said* it to him last night.))
6. Oni *su kazali* da će biti potrebno više vremena. (They *said* it will take more time.)
7. Ti *si rekao* da nećeš doći na sastanak, zar ne? (You *said* you won't come to the meeting, right?)
8. Šta *kažeš* da odemo u kino večeras? (What do *you say* we go to the movies tonight?)
9. *Kazao* sam joj istinu i ispričao sve što se dogodilo. (I told her the truth and explained everything that happened.)
10. Nisam čuo šta si *rekao*. (*Kaži* mi ponovo.) (I didn't hear what you *said*. (Tell me again.))